bookSeries: 五等分の花嫁 / The Quintessential Quintuplets #7
Plot: Finals have arrived for the Quintuplets, but...the Quints' father tries to wall them off once again! Will the Quints finally pass their exams and advance to the next year? Or will they end up repeating past mistakes...and parting ways with Futaro forever? Emotions are at an all-time high in volume 7 of the Quintessential Quintuplets!
